{"tid":614221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「動物保護」店前抗議 野味餐館老闆窗前劏肉「明挑機」","createTime":"2018-04-02T10:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T12:52:12.000Z","uid":12841,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f69d368576b2d06a29996b58fb640c857d8cf9c9","tid":614221,"uid":12841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"外國不少「素食主義者」同「動物保護主義者」經常都有激進抗議行動，好似年頭衝入去澳洲一間牛扒屋抗議，連英國名廚Jamie Oliver都曾經因為在節目介紹過一款牛奶，隨即引起素食者到他旗下餐廳抗議。多倫多就有間野味餐廳，上星期就遇上素食者抗議，不過店主就咁樣回應...<br />\n<br />\n多倫多有家名為「鹿角」（Antler）的野味餐館，菜單上有鵝肝、鴨肝、野味豬、鹿和牛肉，在當地相當有名，適逢3月份是多倫多動物保護月，有「素食主義者」同「動物保護主義者」就在3月23日，到這間野味餐館集會抗議。<br />\n<br />\n不過餐廳老闆Michael Hunter不甘示弱，正當抗議者在店前拉晒Banner，他就拿條鹿腿到餐廳櫥窗前，當著抗議者的面，邊切鹿腿邊食肉，擺明挑機。班抗議者們當然震驚，一副「怎麼可以吃兔兔」的口臉進行抗爭，今次就交戰仲引起廣泛討論，不過網上似乎一面倒抨擊抗議者。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=gourmet&amp;aid=15240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dgourmet%26aid%3D15240&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=545ec278\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=gourmet&amp;aid=15240</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2729536ed7deedcdb17e3d6dc084586d060595e","tid":614221,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"動保根本戇鳩"},{"pid":"bf653b3f93c727300f5d72b496a6d94dfb118f3d","tid":614221,"uid":53568,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"怎麼可以吃兔兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceaa2edb6399458d725675888e022da1e1dd871e","tid":614221,"uid":26179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"班動物膠嬲撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d0436abec47bd6555ff7cd7e2af77d2998a62c","tid":614221,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceaa2edb6399458d725675888e022da1e1dd871e","tid":614221,"uid":26179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"班動物膠嬲撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"睇住佢地又嬲又乜都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c272e89a427a92cff9f5d8a489812f6e1f17ee5f","tid":614221,"uid":11097,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"On撚9<br />\n佢地係人店前示威影響人生意就得<br />\n人地係自己店內切肉就唔撚得<br />\ndouble standard 自私撚<br />\n你試下如果地球上冇人食肉<br />\n地球生態會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feeecf94c5d125883799dc754f978df23284cab","tid":614221,"uid":26238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"啲vegan去一去支那激死都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc701a33083e47017ced5646e67bdea8b5fda34b","tid":614221,"uid":15325,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/184106_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F184106_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=da350cd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8458c8009ebcea68c9d3496e13cf04db0f743170","tid":614221,"uid":12892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"大快人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死素狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/